      <description>As a marketer you know it&amp;#8217;s a fact =  Search engine traffic converts.  Plain and simple and the top dog when it comes to search engine traffic is Google.  Yeah, I know&amp;#8230;another fact.  
There are two ways to get traffic from Google&amp;#8217;s search engine results: 1 - Buy it [...]&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/profit-outlines/Profit_Outlines-Google_Manipulator_-_Guide_to_Free_Google_Search_Traffic.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><a href="http://profitoutlines.com/Go/GoogleManipulator"><img src="http://profitoutlines.com/guides/wp-content/uploads/2008/08/google-manipulator.jpg" alt="" title="google-manipulator" width="192" height="236" class="alignleft size-medium wp-image-69" align="left" border="0" style="margin: 10px;" /></a>  As a marketer you know it&#8217;s a fact =  Search engine traffic converts.  Plain and simple and the top dog when it comes to search engine traffic is Google.  Yeah, I know&#8230;another fact.  </p>
<p>There are two ways to get traffic from Google&#8217;s search engine results: 1 - Buy it via AdWords and 2 - Get your website to rank well for the keywords related to your niche.  Of course, buying the traffic is the easiest but it can get extremely expensive if you&#8217;re bidding on competitive keywords and phrases.</p>
<p>That&#8217;s why, in my opinion, the second option is the best.  Free search engine traffic, targeted to your site and what you&#8217;re offering - frankly, I don&#8217;t think there is anything more profitable in these regards.  The only problem is, how do you do it and do it consistently?</p>
<p>That&#8217;s where <a href="http://profitoutlines.com/Go/GoogleManipulator">Google Manipulator</a> comes in&#8230;.<br />
<span id="more-68"></span><br />
<center><br />
<a href="http://profitoutlines.com/Go/GoogleManipulator"><strong>Click Here to Visit the Google Manipulator<BR>Official Site to Learn more!</strong></a><br />
</center></p>
<p>See, there are people who have ranking well in Google down to an exact science.  I mean they can get pretty much any page they want, on any terms they want - ranked well in the search results and ranking well in search results means traffic: Lots of Traffic.</p>
<p>Pawel Reszka is one of those guys!  He&#8217;s been at it a long time and has proven himself as one of the top guys when it comes to getting good rankings in Google.  By proven himself, I mean to say he gets his stuff ranked well and he has put together guides that others have followed to get their stuff to rank well.</p>
<p>It&#8217;s one thing to be able to get those solid, good rankings in Google for your sites and products but when you can teach people how you do it and they succeed as well - then you clearly have your stuff together and know what you&#8217;re talking about and Pawel Reszka does.</p>
<p>His latest guide is <a href="http://profitoutlines.com/Go/GoogleManipulator">Google Manipulator</a> and in it he shares with you the secrets that work for him to get high up in the search results.  That&#8217;s quite different from others in his field, sure they&#8217;ll sell you a guide and it will probably help you out but at the same time - they don&#8217;t tell you everything.  Pawel does.</p>
<p>In the Google Manipulator Course he provides you with a system that has been tested and proven to get good rankings, but that&#8217;s not all - this course will guide you step by step (by the hand, if you will) through the process of good search engine ranking.</p>
<p>Not only does he teach you how the key things to getting free search engine traffic, but he goes much further than that.  He shows you how to be a solid marketer as well.</p>
<p>Even more, he shows you how to find niches that are virtually untouched and not any ol&#8217; niches either - these are niches that people spend money in but marketers for some reason or another haven&#8217;t really marketed them.  You&#8217;ll also find out the ONE thing you should really avoid when deciding on a niche to enter.</p>
<p>You&#8217;ll also learn how to dig down and find those really profitable long tail key phrases that buyers use to search for the items you&#8217;re selling.  Other things you&#8217;ll get out of this guide are:</p>
<ul>
<li>Proven Cash Making strategies
<li>Profitable Web 2.0 sites
<li>Optimizing your pages the right way
<li>How to get ranked in Google within days, not months
<li>Choosing the right domain name
<li>Creating and using Linkbaits
<li>and there is so much more!
</ul>
<p><a href="http://profitoutlines.com/Go/GoogleManipulator">Google Manipulator</a> is really a great guide, written by someone who knows what they&#8217;re talking about.  Whether you&#8217;re an affiliate marketer or you market your own products, you still need to get good rankings in Google to really be able to take your profit making to another level and Google Manipulator shows you exactly how to do that.</p>
<p><center><br />
<a href="http://profitoutlines.com/Go/GoogleManipulator"><strong>Click Here to Visit the Google Manipulator<BR>Official Site to Learn more!</strong></a><br />
</center></p>
